        "u_description": "\u003Cp\u003E(IFS Customer Priority: High)\u00A0\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003E*MIT is currently working on placing labels on the Storeroom\u0026#39;s racks.\u00A0 So far no label has been properly printed.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u00A0\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThe Parts Description is not properly displayed, it cuts half of the description in the Label.\u00A0 This can be seen from the Preview and also when Printed.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThe section where the location No. have a issue, it doesn\u0026#39;t show all the location No.\u003Cbr /\u003E\u003Cbr /\u003EPlease see the attachments\u00A0\u003Cbr /\u003E\u003Cbr /\u003EIn this case the location No. for the part 105396 is CRANES-04-B-25-03\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\r\n\u003Cdiv\u003EBut in the printed label just appear CRANES-04-B-25 the last 3 digits are missing in every part we try to print the barcode.\u003C/div\u003E\r\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u00A0\u003C/div\u003E\r\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003ESteps to Preview/Print:\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Col style=\u0022list-style-position: inside;\u0022\u003E\u003Cli\u003EGo to: \u0026#34;Inventory Parts in Stock\u0026#34;.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003ESearch for Sample Part: \u003Cstrong\u003E105396\u003C/strong\u003E.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003ESelect the line with the Part you want to Print, Then at the top menu click the Buton \u0026#34;Print\u0026#34; will show.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EClick Print then click \u0026#34;Print Barcode Labels\u0026#34;.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EClick OK to continue.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EClick Yes to Print without Preview.\u00A0 To Preview: Click No to go to Next Screen then Click Preview.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ol\u003E\r\n\u003C/div\u003E\r\n\u003C/div\u003E",
