                "PlainTextDescription": null,
                "RichTextDescription": "\u003Cp\u003EThe Label displays fine in IFS Preview, but the Printed label cuts long Locations when Printed.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EIm checking with Local MIT Service Desk Team, if there may be any possible way of modifying/setup printer borders limit.\u0026nbsp; If this is not possible the Report would need to be checked/modified to properly Print.\u003C/p\u003E\r\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESteps to Preview/Print:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\r\u003Col style=\u0022list-style-position: inside;\u0022\u003E\u003Cli\u003EGo to: Inventory Parts in Stock.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003ESearch for Part: \u003Cstrong\u003E105396.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003ESelect the line with the Part: \u003Cstrong\u003E105396,\u0026nbsp;\u003C/strong\u003EAt the top the Buton \u003Cstrong\u003E\u0022Print\u0022\u003C/strong\u003E will show.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EClick \u003Cstrong\u003EPrint \u003C/strong\u003Ethen click \u003Cstrong\u003E\u0022Print Barcode Labels\u0022.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EClick OK to continue.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EClick \u003Cstrong\u003EYes \u003C/strong\u003Eto Print without Preview.\u0026nbsp; To Preview: Click \u003Cstrong\u003ENo \u003C/strong\u003Eto go to Next Screen then Click Preview.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ol\u003E\r\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022/sys_attachment.do?sys_id=30eea0e3c30e4a50702f2f2bb00131be\u0022 alt=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E",
